snippet.title: GLBX Lunch & Learn: LGBTQ Protections and the Upcoming Florida Legislative Session
snippet.description:
On March 3, 2021, the Greater Fort Lauderdale Chamber of Commerce's GLBX Council partnered with Equality Florida to provide an update on bills being considered by lawmakers in Tallahassee, concerning LGBTQ protections.

GLBX Council Chair Rene Cantu was joined by Jon Harris Maurer, Public Policy Director for Equality Florida.
